(250, 0, 'Rose Food Fertilizer for Rose Plant (500gms)', 'simple', 'RFF-1980', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\\n  <li>?Useful for all types of garden plants & Roses.</li>\r\\n  <li><i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>?Mix with the potting media or directly apply on Potted & Garden Plants.</li>\r\\n  <li><i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>?Repeat fertilizers between 30 to 45 days.</li>\r\\n  <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">100% Organic, complete care for your rose plants boosts branching and flowering</span></li>\r\\n  <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">When topping up soil for potted plant, apply 40-50 gm before watering the plant during early morning or late evening. Water the plants immediately after the application.</span></li>\r\\n  <li>Ingrediants: Neem powder, sarso powder, bone meal, DAP, and vermicompost.</li>\r\\n</ul>', '<div class=\"spr-review-content\">\r\\n<p class=\"spr-review-content-body\">Highly recommend this product to encourage flower budding and growth of new shoots. Need to put only a tablespoon per plant every week or fortnight. Have seen my roses bloom like anything and also seen new stem growth on other plants. After putting this on the topsoil, water your plants immediately. Don\'t exceed dosage by more than once a week. Just need a little bit every week or every other week.</p>\r\\n\r\\n</div>\r\\n<div class=\"spr-review-footer\"></div>', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '199', 'Fertilizers, Manure, rose food-fertilizer, rose plant fertilizer', '', '', '', '', '', 'rose-food-fertilizer-for-rose-plant-500gms', ''),
