(676, 0, 'Ming Fern, Asparagus Macowanii - Plant', 'simple', 'MING10110', '<ul>\r\\n  <li>Plant?s height with a pot approximately 3 feet and pot size 6 inches.</li>\r\\n  <li>The plants can grow around the year.</li>\r\\n  <li>The plant is useful for air purifying, home decor, garden decor, and gift purposes.</li>\r\\n  <li>it?s a Non-Flowering plant and recommended by air-purifying plants can survive indoor and semi-shade conditions.</li>\r\\n</ul>', '<h3><strong>Ming Fern, Asparagus Macowanii ?- Plant</strong></h3>\r\\nMing Asparagus Fern Plants have the finest foliage of all the asparagus ferns. The leaves resemble fennel leaves. Maintains its foliage indoors in bright indirect light.\r\\n\r\\n<a href=\"https://www.calyxflowers.com/floral-library/ming-fern/\">Ming Fern</a>(Asparagus macowanii). Despite its name, the ming fern is a flowering plant and not a fern at all. It produces white flowers in the spring to early summer. It is in the same genus as the edible cultivated perennial vegetable, Asparagus Officinalis. Ming Ferns do well in full sun as well as in shaded locations. A native to arid regions of South Africa, this is a very drought tolerant plant. It can reach a height of 4-6? when grown in the ground, but can also be grown in containers to achieve a much smaller plant. It is an excellent house plant.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Height:</strong>?can grow to 4+ feet. Fertilize during spring and summer. Arching perennial Soil Conditions: Just about any Plant has spines or sharp edges.\r\\n<strong>Light Exposure:</strong> Bright indirect light.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Water: </strong>Ming Asparagus Fern Plants likes to stay moist. It does not like to stay or sit in water or get too dry. This plant will tolerate some drought but may lose some of its needles.\r\\n<strong>Colour:</strong>?Green Produces seed, not spores/ asparagus fern\r\\n<strong>Flowers:</strong>?white flowers Unique growth habit\r\\n<strong>Uses</strong> Groundcover, Large containers, or hanging baskets. This plant is attractive to bees, butterflies, and/or birds\r\\n<strong>HARDINESS:</strong>?Zone 9 to 11\r\\n<strong>Re-potting Tips:</strong> Re-pot one size larger Water regularly, but take care not to over-water by allowing the top 3 inches of soil to dry out between waterings. Water sparingly in winter, but do not allow the soil to dry out completely. Fertilizer: good well-balanced plant food (10-10-10)\r\\n<strong>Indoor Lighting:</strong> bright light Humidity: prefers moist air. Temperature: Average room temperatures 60-75?F\r\\n<strong>Soil:</strong>?good potting mix Outdoor Hardy Zone 9 temperatures(25-30 ?F)', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '799', '950', 'Asparagus Macowanii, Asparagus macowanii var. zuluensis, Asparagus zuluensis, chinese ming fern, Green Asparagus, Green Asparagus Racemosus Plant, Ming Fern, Protasparagus macowanii, shatavari', '', '', '', '', '', 'ming-fern-asparagus-macowanii-plant', ''),
(677, 0, 'Dracaena \"Cordyline fruticosa\", Baby Doll Plant', 'simple', 'DBD310', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\\n  <li>Live plant along with the plastic pot.</li>\r\\n  <li><i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Plants? height with pot is 20? to 24 inches & pot size is 6 inches in diameter.</li>\r\\n  <li><i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Plants? nature is outdoor-semi shade, alternate day watering.</li>\r\\n  <li>Evergreen perennial shrub in the family.</li>\r\\n  <li>The most attractive & beautiful plant for the garden.<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></li>\r\\n</ul>', '<h3>Dracaena Baby Doll Plant</h3>\r\\nDracaena Baby Doll Plant is an evergreen perennial shrub in the family. Attractive fan-like and spirally arranged cluster of broadly elongated leaves at the tip of the slender trunk. Dracaena is a group of popular plants which can be grown both <a href=\"https://nurserynisarga.in/product-category/indoorplant/\">indoors</a> and <a href=\"https://nurserynisarga.in/product-category/outdoorplant/\">outdoor</a>-based on climatic conditions.\r\\n\r\\nThey are known for easy care, maintenance, and beautiful foliage (leaves). Originating from Southeast Asia, it is known for its striking colouring, which can vary from purple-pink to deep Green. Different varieties possess different coloured foliage. Dracaena Baby Doll Plant is a very decorative', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '499', '549', 'cordyline, Cordyline fruticosa, Dracaena Baby Doll, Dracaena cordyline', '', '', '', '', '', 'dracaena-cordyline-fruticosa-baby-doll-plant', '');
