of indoor and outdoor plants.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Care-?</strong>Wipe out with soft and dry cloth, store in a clean and dry place, but handle with firm hands.', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '599', '625', 'Bonsai Pot, Bonsai Tray', '', '', '', '', '', 'bonsai-oval-plastic-tray-set-of-3', ''),
