(1036, 0, 'Pack of 5 Guava Plant', 'simple', 'GUAPACK-102-1', 'This pack contains Fruit Plant for Terrace/Open garden. Best plants for Planting fruit trees could prove to be the most fruitful effort in your <a href=\"https://parenting.firstcry.com/articles/magazine-10-surprising-benefits-of-gardening-growing-plants-is-beyond-just-a-good-hobby/?ref=interlink\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">gardening</a> endeavour. With their lush foliage, fragrant flowers, and nectar-like harvest, small fruit trees in your tiny garden could be the best investment for your home.\r\\n<ul>\r\\n  <li>Get organic food</li>\r\\n  <li>Easy to care for.</li>\r\\n</ul>', '<div>\r\\n<h2>Pack of 5 Guava Plant</h2>\r\\n<h3>What makes it special</h3>\r\\n<a href=\"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/home-garden/7-fruit-trees-you-can-grow-in-your-homes/photostory/61484829.cms\">Growing Fruits at home</a> is possible now! We Indians enjoy including fruits in our daily life. These plants are popular not only as fruits but of them also famous for their <a href=\"https://nurserynisarga.in/?s=medicinal+plant&post_type=product&dgwt_wcas=1\">medicinal</a> benefits. Pack of best 5 Guava Plant for Terrace/Open garden. These plants are elementary to take care of, require very low maintenance, and can be grown outdoors with full sunlight. These plants also purify the air where they live.\r\\n<h4>Care instructions</h4>\r\\nPlace the plant in open full sunlight.\r\\nDo not overwater the plant, or water when the upper soil seems dry.\r\\nRemove dead, infected or damaged plant parts\r\\nFertilize your plant with organic fertilizer.\r\\n<h4 class=\"nl-h2\">What you get</h4>\r\\n</div>\r\\n<table class=\"nl-prod-desc-table\" xss=removed width=\"604\">\r\\n<tbody>\r\\n<tr>\r\\n<th>Name</th>\r\\n<th>Quantity</th>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr>\r\\n<td><a href=\"https://nurserynisarga.in/product/thai-guava-grafted-guava-amrud-psidium-guajav-plant/\">Thai Guava, Grafted Guava, Amrud, Psidium guajav ? Plant</a></td